&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Kobler HIV outpatients team based on Fulham road are looking for a motivated and enthusiastic nurse for an exciting permanent B5 post &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for someone who is experienced, motivated, has a great work ethic and who possesses excellent interpersonal and communication skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are ideally looking for someone who has experience in HIV outpatients or inpatients or a nurse who has a keen interest in developing their skills and knowledge within the specialty to work with a diverse range of clients in an innovative outpatients HIV setting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Working flexibly the post holder will ensure that their team provides a gold standard, patient focused service at all times.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Although the post may in future involve some rotational work in John Hunter Clinic for sexual health, it will be primarily based in Kobler HIV OPD.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
